text: Ate musa ne kiha, he sade raba! Tusim phira'auna vala unham de saradaram nu duni'avi jivana vica raja sata, samana ate dhana dita hai. He sade raba! Isa la'i ki uha tere raha tom lokam nu bhataka'una. He sade raba! Inham di ja'idada nu nasata kara de ate inham de dilam nu inham sakhata bana de ki iha loka imana na li'a'una ethom taka ki iha daradanaka saza nu dekha lena
